-- Abu Dhabi Islamic Bank Second-Quarter Profit Jumps 56% as Provisions Drop
-- Arif Sharif
-- 2010-07-18T11:57:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-18/abu-dhabi-islamic-bank-second-quarter-profit-jumps-56-as-provisions-drop.html

          
          
             Abu Dhabi Islamic Bank posted a 56
percent increase in second-quarter profit to 301.6 million
dirhams compared with the year-earlier period, according to an
e-mailed statement today.  
